1
00:01:30,580 --> 00:01:36,970
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}EPISODE 12: 
LIZE, THE BLACK WITCH'S APPRENTICE</font>

2
00:01:33,640 --> 00:01:35,030
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Well, this is a surprise.</font>

3
00:01:35,270 --> 00:01:38,360
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I did not expect Henri to drop 
in with Luna and her friends.</font>

4
00:01:39,080 --> 00:01:40,700
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I apologize for intruding,</font>

5
00:01:40,930 --> 00:01:44,030
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">but this is the only truly 
safe place I could think of.</font>

6
00:01:44,340 --> 00:01:48,430
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I don't mind. We are protected 
by a very strong barrier here.</font>

7
00:01:48,840 --> 00:01:49,910
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Even the royal family</font>

8
00:01:49,910 --> 00:01:53,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">cannot communicate with us here, 
nor enter without my permission.</font>

9
00:01:54,510 --> 00:01:59,610
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You made the best decision for 
protecting them. You have my thanks.</font>

10
00:01:59,610 --> 00:02:01,390
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Um, I'm honored.</font>

11
00:02:01,610 --> 00:02:08,150
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">By the way, Master Bird, about this... 
official? This part-white magician?</font>

12
00:02:08,150 --> 00:02:09,650
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">How do you know him?</font>

13
00:02:09,650 --> 00:02:12,130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">He is my blood relative.</font>

14
00:02:12,500 --> 00:02:16,120
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The same white magician 
blood runs in our veins,</font>

15
00:02:16,120 --> 00:02:20,160
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">but he has agreed to perform certain 
tasks for the black magicians.</font>

16
00:02:22,410 --> 00:02:26,910
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">He assists me in various ways, 
as I live secretly as a black magician</font>

17
00:02:26,910 --> 00:02:29,420
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">inside the white witches' royal palace.</font>

18
00:02:30,170 --> 00:02:34,930
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We are both in precarious positions, 
but he performs his duties diligently.</font>

19
00:02:36,070 --> 00:02:37,230
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Henri...</i></font>

20
00:02:37,850 --> 00:02:42,970
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">As I cannot use magic, I don't think 
I've been particularly helpful.</font>

21
00:02:42,970 --> 00:02:45,390
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But while I do not understand why,</font>

22
00:02:45,800 --> 00:02:49,660
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I have this nagging feeling that I can't 
ignore the plight of the black witches.</font>

23
00:02:50,280 --> 00:02:54,130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Even if it puts my life at risk, I want 
to do whatever I can to help them.</font>

24
00:02:55,730 --> 00:02:58,650
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Huh, so that's what you're about.</font>

25
00:02:58,650 --> 00:03:02,670
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Well, Master Bird himself is already 
an anomaly as a white witch,</font>

26
00:03:02,670 --> 00:03:04,910
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">so I guess this isn't any stranger.</font>

27
00:03:05,460 --> 00:03:09,660
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>This connection between 
them is suffocating me.</i></font>

28
00:03:10,390 --> 00:03:13,230
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Even if I try to look away, 
I can't help but see it.</i></font>

29
00:03:13,640 --> 00:03:16,290
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I, on the contrary, 
am weak enough to disappear.</i></font>

30
00:03:16,680 --> 00:03:22,180
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I sense such a strong bond between them...
 I don't want to see any more!</i></font>

31
00:03:23,150 --> 00:03:27,090
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">By the way, Wind, were you able 
to fulfill your duty regarding</font>

32
00:03:27,090 --> 00:03:29,550
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The End of All Things without incident?</font>

33
00:03:29,870 --> 00:03:30,310
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Huh?</font>

34
00:03:35,810 --> 00:03:40,080
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I see. You shredded its poisoned 
skin into smaller pieces</font>

35
00:03:36,170 --> 00:03:38,840
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}Ouch! Ouch! Ouch!</font>

36
00:03:40,080 --> 00:03:41,550
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">and scattered them everywhere.</font>

37
00:03:40,630 --> 00:03:44,090
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}There was nothing else I could do!</font>

38
00:03:44,500 --> 00:03:48,370
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It was pretty much a corpse 
anyway, so what's the harm?</font>

39
00:03:49,170 --> 00:03:52,330
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Huh? Don't look at me like that, guys.</font>

40
00:03:52,330 --> 00:03:56,470
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I see. So you spread the seeds 
of The End even further.</font>

41
00:03:56,470 --> 00:03:58,360
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What an absolute catastrophe.</font>

42
00:03:58,870 --> 00:04:03,480
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Breathing that air has clearly 
taken a toll on Lize, as well.</font>

43
00:04:05,000 --> 00:04:06,860
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I only spread a little bit!</font>

44
00:04:06,860 --> 00:04:11,450
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I made sure to send all the rest to Flame 
and Stoney with wind teleportation!</font>

45
00:04:09,160 --> 00:04:13,100
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}POISON (END OF ALL THINGS) CLEANUP CREW</font>

46
00:04:09,160 --> 00:04:13,100
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}CRYSTAL WITCH | FLAME MAGICIAN</font>

47
00:04:11,450 --> 00:04:14,630
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I mean, you were all asking 
way too much of me, anyway!</font>

48
00:04:14,630 --> 00:04:18,620
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Miss Luna, would you quit inventing 
scary faces to glare at me with? Please!</font>

49
00:04:18,620 --> 00:04:23,740
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Today is the first time I've met black 
magicians other than Miss Witch,</i></font>

50
00:04:23,740 --> 00:04:25,700
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>but this Wind Magician...</i></font>

51
00:04:23,740 --> 00:04:26,310
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}Wow! Look, now you're all doing it!</font>

52
00:04:25,700 --> 00:04:29,990
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>seems to have no problem at all
 flaunting ethical standards.</i></font>

53
00:04:26,310 --> 00:04:29,990
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}Come on, guys. Somebody 
say something! Please!</font>

54
00:04:29,990 --> 00:04:35,120
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">C'mon! Why're you all picking on me?! 
Do you know what I've been through?!</font>

55
00:04:35,120 --> 00:04:39,130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It isn't like Miss Luna and Master Bird 
are doing poison collection-slash-cleanup!</font>

56
00:04:39,130 --> 00:04:41,880
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Slaying The End of All Things 
and hauling all that poison</font>

57
00:04:41,880 --> 00:04:44,510
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}REBEL WITHOUT A CAUSE</font>

58
00:04:41,880 --> 00:04:44,510
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">is super rough work and it's 
scary and really stressful!</font>

59
00:04:43,610 --> 00:04:44,510
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}ADULTS JUST DON'T UNDERSTAND</font>

60
00:04:44,800 --> 00:04:48,130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I put my life on the line fighting 
a monster and you want me to be delicate?</font>

61
00:04:48,130 --> 00:04:49,250
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Gimme a break!</font>

62
00:04:49,250 --> 00:04:51,630
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">There's some things in life 
you just can't do perfectly!</font>

63
00:04:51,630 --> 00:04:56,910
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But you all stand there judging me from 
a safe distance like you're above me!</font>

64
00:04:56,910 --> 00:04:59,230
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That's not what we're cringing at, though.</font>

65
00:04:59,230 --> 00:05:03,690
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Do you have a right to attack me just 
'cause I do things a little different?!</font>

66
00:05:03,690 --> 00:05:05,450
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I suppose that's true.</font>

67
00:05:05,450 --> 00:05:09,470
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Wind has a good point. Perhaps 
we should leave criticism</font>

68
00:05:09,470 --> 00:05:13,620
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">to the two in charge of disposing 
of The End of All Things instead.</font>

69
00:05:09,830 --> 00:05:11,770
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{\an8}Emotional abuse.</i></font>

70
00:05:13,620 --> 00:05:15,490
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{\an8}Emotional abuse.</i></font>

71
00:05:13,620 --> 00:05:16,270
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Surely they are in a better 
position to judge than we are.</font>

72
00:05:17,050 --> 00:05:18,830
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{\an8}Emotional abuse.</i></font>

73
00:05:22,010 --> 00:05:26,670
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I didn't realize black witches all 
take on different roles like that.</i></font>

74
00:05:27,000 --> 00:05:28,970
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Like slaying The End of All Things...</i></font>

75
00:05:31,580 --> 00:05:35,980
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Master Bird, I should take my leave now. 
My supervisor must be looking for me.</font>

76
00:05:35,980 --> 00:05:39,610
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Very well. Thank you for 
everything. And be careful.</font>

77
00:05:39,900 --> 00:05:43,550
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">To be safe, I will cast a fake 
shield over your memories.</font>

78
00:05:43,550 --> 00:05:44,890
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Thank you very much.</font>

79
00:05:46,540 --> 00:05:48,430
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Well then, Luna,</font>

80
00:05:49,060 --> 00:05:50,180
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">farewell.</font>

81
00:05:51,860 --> 00:05:54,620
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I very much enjoyed meeting you.</font>

82
00:05:55,050 --> 00:05:59,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I pray that I will find you again 
someday, happy and healthy.</font>

83
00:06:02,620 --> 00:06:03,880
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Miss Luna.</font>

84
00:06:05,770 --> 00:06:10,010
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm real sorry for throwing a fit 
like that. But do you think...</font>

85
00:06:10,550 --> 00:06:12,490
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">you could do your thing for me, maybe?</font>

86
00:06:14,770 --> 00:06:16,170
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Of course.</font>

87
00:06:20,310 --> 00:06:24,070
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I've been too busy to 
come see you recently,</font>

88
00:06:24,070 --> 00:06:26,620
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">so I'm sorry I let it get this bad.</font>

89
00:06:28,840 --> 00:06:30,420
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's no trouble at all.</font>

90
00:06:46,770 --> 00:06:49,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You must have suffered greatly
 if you contracted this much.</font>

91
00:06:51,780 --> 00:06:56,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Poison magicians are much more 
capable of tolerating and coexisting</font>

92
00:06:56,380 --> 00:07:01,730
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">with poison than most, but that does not 
mean they have total control over it.</font>

93
00:07:03,190 --> 00:07:05,650
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Luna is the exception.</font>

94
00:07:06,070 --> 00:07:09,660
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The rest must carry out their 
duties tainted with poison.</font>

95
00:07:11,030 --> 00:07:15,670
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>The poisonous mushrooms, of all 
different shapes and colors,</i></font>

96
00:07:16,020 --> 00:07:19,580
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>almost resembled a cradle protecting Wind,</i></font>

97
00:07:20,180 --> 00:07:23,150
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>and for a moment, appeared very beautiful.</i></font>

98
00:07:24,170 --> 00:07:27,810
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm sorry for being so patronizing before.</font>

99
00:07:27,810 --> 00:07:29,970
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I truly am grateful for all you've done.</font>

100
00:07:30,470 --> 00:07:31,990
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Then,</i></font>

101
00:07:31,990 --> 00:07:36,440
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>as if they had been watching over Wind 
as he slept in a great mushroom forest,</i></font>

102
00:07:36,910 --> 00:07:40,860
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>the mushrooms floated up gently 
into the air and then disappeared.</i></font>

103
00:07:42,490 --> 00:07:45,230
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Phew! I'm reborn!</font>

104
00:07:45,730 --> 00:07:49,140
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">My body feels so light!
It feels like I grew wings!</font>

105
00:07:49,140 --> 00:07:50,990
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Thanks, Miss Luna!</font>

106
00:07:50,990 --> 00:07:53,990
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm very glad that I was able to help.</font>

107
00:07:54,220 --> 00:07:55,230
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh...</font>

108
00:07:56,250 --> 00:08:02,040
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Whoa, whoops. Whenever Miss Luna smiles 
at me, I get this tingly feeling inside.</font>

109
00:08:02,040 --> 00:08:06,860
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Miss Witch, can you cure any kind of 
ailment by turning it into a mushroom</font>

110
00:08:06,860 --> 00:08:08,090
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">and then removing it?</font>

111
00:08:08,570 --> 00:08:11,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Sometimes, ailments are 
bound to a person's destiny,</font>

112
00:08:12,370 --> 00:08:16,040
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">so I can't turn just anything 
into a mushroom and take it out.</font>

113
00:08:16,040 --> 00:08:21,100
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">In those cases, I can either 
leave it there as an ailment</font>

114
00:08:21,500 --> 00:08:25,850
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">or try to force it out, but when 
I do that it comes at a price.</font>

115
00:08:26,340 --> 00:08:27,640
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Price?</i></font>

116
00:08:29,110 --> 00:08:34,110
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Now that the other guy left and we know 
Miss Luna's powers are back to normal,</font>

117
00:08:34,340 --> 00:08:37,230
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">why don't you and I have a little chat?</font>

118
00:08:38,340 --> 00:08:40,820
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">And then I'll make my decision.</font>

119
00:08:41,250 --> 00:08:45,460
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">This is a final interview that will 
determine if you pass or fail.</font>

120
00:08:48,760 --> 00:08:52,150
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I think you know this by now, 
but a cursed youngling is basically an egg</font>

121
00:08:52,150 --> 00:08:53,890
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">that grows into The End of All Things.</font>

122
00:08:54,490 --> 00:08:58,260
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">So look, Lize, if this keeps up, you're 
gonna turn into The End yourself.</font>

123
00:09:15,730 --> 00:09:18,530
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Lize? Lize!</font>

124
00:09:20,740 --> 00:09:26,160
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm guessing that shocked face means
 nobody told you anything, right?</font>

125
00:09:26,460 --> 00:09:31,010
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm sure they had their reasons not 
to tell you the truth about all this,</font>

126
00:09:31,500 --> 00:09:34,440
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">but we won't get anywhere 
if you know nothing,</font>

127
00:09:34,440 --> 00:09:37,260
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">so I made the call to tell you myself.</font>

128
00:09:37,560 --> 00:09:44,020
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I always suspected something. I didn't 
want to believe it was true, though.</font>

129
00:09:44,380 --> 00:09:48,410
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>A cursed youngling is one destined 
to become The End of All Things...</i></font>

130
00:09:48,410 --> 00:09:52,850
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>You are the one who should 
never have been born.</i></font>

131
00:09:54,810 --> 00:09:55,560
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Huh?</font>

132
00:09:56,270 --> 00:09:56,990
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh.</font>

133
00:09:57,790 --> 00:09:58,630
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What?</font>

134
00:09:59,130 --> 00:10:02,850
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Man, you're always sinking 
into darkness. What a pain.</font>

135
00:10:04,120 --> 00:10:06,530
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Would you mind snapping outta 
 that self-pity for me?</font>

136
00:10:06,530 --> 00:10:07,770
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I've got a job to do here.</font>

137
00:10:08,670 --> 00:10:12,670
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>He has so little empathy and 
compassion, it's almost shocking.</i></font>

138
00:10:12,670 --> 00:10:13,670
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What's that?</font>

139
00:10:14,010 --> 00:10:15,030
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Nothing.</font>

140
00:10:15,030 --> 00:10:18,670
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>But right now, I think 
that's exactly what I need.</i></font>

141
00:10:16,600 --> 00:10:18,170
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}So listen, Lize,</font>

142
00:10:18,670 --> 00:10:21,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}you're totally, pointlessly head 
over heels for Luna, right?</font>

143
00:10:21,790 --> 00:10:23,770
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Ugh. Totally insensitive, too.</i></font>

144
00:10:23,770 --> 00:10:26,180
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Wait. Did you think nobody noticed?</font>

145
00:10:26,180 --> 00:10:29,820
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You reek so badly of infatuation, 
even a total idiot could tell.</font>

146
00:10:30,310 --> 00:10:35,070
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>This isn't good. I can't spend all my 
time cataloging other people's faults.</i></font>

147
00:10:35,070 --> 00:10:39,540
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">So have you also not realized what 
kind of a spot that puts Miss Luna in?</font>

148
00:10:40,020 --> 00:10:43,330
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I can't bear it. Talking to 
this guy is too frustrating.</i></font>

149
00:10:43,330 --> 00:10:47,450
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You're definitely hard-headed 
enough to be a white witch, kid.</font>

150
00:10:47,450 --> 00:10:52,040
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But look, you need to smother that 
crush of yours once and for all.</font>

151
00:10:52,580 --> 00:10:54,950
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's never going to blossom, anyway.</font>

152
00:10:55,340 --> 00:10:59,260
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I want you to tear it out while it's 
still a bud. You get me, right?</font>

153
00:10:59,260 --> 00:11:04,140
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>For black witches, love is a poison
 that weakens their magic.</i></font>

154
00:11:05,340 --> 00:11:09,180
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But like you just said, 
isn't it completely one-sided?</font>

155
00:11:09,180 --> 00:11:10,590
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Well, yeah.</font>

156
00:11:10,980 --> 00:11:15,520
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">If your crush on her was 
the reason she was struggling,</font>

157
00:11:15,520 --> 00:11:18,900
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">test or no test, I would 
have killed you on the spot.</font>

158
00:11:19,170 --> 00:11:23,160
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But the cause turned out to be another 
person, so you're off the hook.</font>

159
00:11:23,260 --> 00:11:29,060
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}GLOOM</font>

160
00:11:24,070 --> 00:11:26,440
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Huh? Is that something 
to get depressed about?</font>

161
00:11:26,440 --> 00:11:28,930
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You sure love basking in doom and gloom!</font>

162
00:11:29,650 --> 00:11:34,670
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Even then, even if it meant my 
death, I wish it had been me.</i></font>

163
00:11:34,670 --> 00:11:40,610
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}GLOOM</font>

164
00:11:34,670 --> 00:11:39,460
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But to be honest, there's another 
reason I couldn't just kill you off.</font>

165
00:11:39,940 --> 00:11:43,870
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Anyway, if you don't want to die, 
you need to strengthen your magic,</font>

166
00:11:43,870 --> 00:11:45,580
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">and learn to stand on your own.</font>

167
00:11:46,140 --> 00:11:50,500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That is, if you wanna escape your fate 
as a cursed youngling, like Miss Luna did.</font>

168
00:11:51,100 --> 00:11:54,260
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Maybe it was starting to drive me crazy.</i></font>

169
00:11:55,170 --> 00:12:00,990
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>When I found out she had been cursed 
just like me, I thought it was fate.</i></font>

170
00:12:00,990 --> 00:12:05,450
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>This joy I secretly felt 
became a sliver of hope.</i></font>

171
00:12:05,870 --> 00:12:11,100
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>This solitude that she could never 
share somehow both saved me</i></font>

172
00:12:11,100 --> 00:12:12,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>and devastated me.</i></font>

173
00:12:13,160 --> 00:12:16,840
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Even while knowing that love 
is poison for Miss Witch,</i></font>

174
00:12:16,840 --> 00:12:19,850
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I dearly wish to become 
the one there to protect her</i></font>

175
00:12:20,180 --> 00:12:24,550
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>and to heal the wounds she 
carries. I want to be the one.</i></font>

176
00:12:24,890 --> 00:12:29,100
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Even if I can't touch her,
 I want to stay by her side always.</i></font>

177
00:12:29,100 --> 00:12:33,230
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>And even now, I can't 
change the way I feel!</i></font>

178
00:12:33,230 --> 00:12:36,990
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">White witches are gross! 
Even after what I said,</font>

179
00:12:36,990 --> 00:12:39,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">you're still getting off on 
your nasty little love poems?</font>

180
00:12:39,380 --> 00:12:43,410
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That's so egotistical... 
it absolutely reeks.</font>

181
00:12:46,150 --> 00:12:49,590
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Someone like you would never understand.</font>

182
00:12:49,960 --> 00:12:54,180
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">A black magician who's never 
even liked another person</font>

183
00:12:54,180 --> 00:12:58,040
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">wouldn't understand the first thing 
about the joy and pain of love.</font>

184
00:12:58,410 --> 00:13:00,720
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You force people's feelings 
into simplistic categories</font>

185
00:13:00,720 --> 00:13:03,550
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">and then try to knock them 
down and mock them one by one.</font>

186
00:13:04,010 --> 00:13:08,450
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Quit acting like you've figured me out!</font>

187
00:13:09,720 --> 00:13:13,180
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You're missing the point. 
Are you good, dude?</font>

188
00:13:13,610 --> 00:13:17,900
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You sure like to ramble, though. I mean, 
it's fine if that burns off some poison.</font>

189
00:13:19,590 --> 00:13:21,730
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">There is one thing I want to ask you.</font>

190
00:13:22,750 --> 00:13:25,950
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Do you really think a life 
without love is that terrible?</font>

191
00:13:26,490 --> 00:13:27,450
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Huh?</font>

192
00:13:27,450 --> 00:13:33,060
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Would it make you feel incomplete as a 
person? Is it something to be ashamed of?</font>

193
00:13:33,400 --> 00:13:34,450
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Uh...</font>

194
00:13:34,700 --> 00:13:38,590
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Do people who've never been 
in love not even matter?</font>

195
00:13:39,400 --> 00:13:40,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I don't know the answer to that.</font>

196
00:13:41,530 --> 00:13:44,080
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But I don't need to 
hear you of all people,</font>

197
00:13:44,080 --> 00:13:45,720
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">a kid who spends every day with Luna,</font>

198
00:13:46,260 --> 00:13:49,660
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">trash talking people for not knowing love.</font>

199
00:13:51,610 --> 00:13:55,290
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">She's unable to love for 
reasons beyond her control.</font>

200
00:13:55,290 --> 00:14:00,720
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">So what you're doing is like 
selfishly backing her into a corner</font>

201
00:14:00,720 --> 00:14:04,900
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">and forcing her to accept bouquets of 
thorny flowers that slice up her hands.</font>

202
00:14:10,260 --> 00:14:12,400
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Now</i> you decide to start crying?</font>

203
00:14:12,400 --> 00:14:13,910
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Whoa, somethin' came outta that brooch!</font>

204
00:14:14,460 --> 00:14:17,590
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>When she's bound by so many chains</i></font>

205
00:14:17,590 --> 00:14:20,630
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>shackling her to a fate that allows her
 no freedom to begin with,</i></font>

206
00:14:21,630 --> 00:14:26,340
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I can't keep clinging to my love 
for her like a selfish child.</i></font>

207
00:14:26,340 --> 00:14:28,170
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I have no right to be with her.</i></font>

208
00:14:29,580 --> 00:14:30,950
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm sorry.</font>

209
00:14:32,620 --> 00:14:34,090
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm sorry!</font>

210
00:14:48,540 --> 00:14:51,370
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Y'know, a long time ago,</font>

211
00:14:51,370 --> 00:14:55,120
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">there was someone you could say 
I had something like a crush on.</font>

212
00:14:55,590 --> 00:14:56,310
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Huh?</font>

213
00:14:56,680 --> 00:14:58,620
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What, is that so shocking?</font>

214
00:14:59,310 --> 00:15:01,810
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I was torn between my 
feelings and my duties,</font>

215
00:15:02,200 --> 00:15:04,130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">and of course, it messed with my magic.</font>

216
00:15:04,130 --> 00:15:05,190
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Heh.</font>

217
00:15:05,190 --> 00:15:07,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hey, don't laugh at me.</font>

218
00:15:07,380 --> 00:15:09,250
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That's so rude!</font>

219
00:15:09,250 --> 00:15:12,390
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Anyway, I got so confused, I even 
considered quitting being a black witch,</font>

220
00:15:12,900 --> 00:15:16,770
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">but she wasn't someone I could 
have that easily anyway.</font>

221
00:15:16,930 --> 00:15:22,630
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">So I decided to cast a wind spell on my 
feelings and scatter them to the winds.</font>

222
00:15:23,340 --> 00:15:26,520
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'd scattered tons of other 
things to the winds by then,</font>

223
00:15:27,300 --> 00:15:30,670
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">and watched all those different 
things as they drifted away from me,</font>

224
00:15:38,520 --> 00:15:43,850
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">but none of them were 
as beautiful as that was.</font>

225
00:15:46,860 --> 00:15:51,090
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Watching my feelings float away 
did make me kind of sad,</font>

226
00:15:51,090 --> 00:15:54,970
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">but it made me realize I actually 
had something beautiful inside me.</font>

227
00:15:56,630 --> 00:16:00,670
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I thought I'd been scarred by 
the horrible things I'd witnessed,</font>

228
00:16:00,670 --> 00:16:03,140
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">so I realized maybe there's 
still hope for me.</font>

229
00:16:03,420 --> 00:16:08,130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It made me realize that all people in love
 have something pretty inside of them.</font>

230
00:16:08,570 --> 00:16:11,570
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Suddenly, the resentment
 I'd clung to for being forced</font>

231
00:16:11,570 --> 00:16:15,160
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">into the thankless work of
 protecting people just disappeared.</font>

232
00:16:15,570 --> 00:16:19,890
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">So my love was gone, 
but in it's place I was left with</font>

233
00:16:20,350 --> 00:16:22,530
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">a little bit of a bigger heart.</font>

234
00:16:23,430 --> 00:16:26,170
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Well, bigger than I'd had before, anyway.</font>

235
00:16:28,110 --> 00:16:29,480
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Now, don't you dare</font>

236
00:16:30,470 --> 00:16:33,230
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">go around telling that story 
to other black magicians, okay?</font>

237
00:16:36,740 --> 00:16:37,600
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yeah, that's right.</font>

238
00:16:37,930 --> 00:16:42,530
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I guess that means you and 
I are partners in crime now.</font>

239
00:16:47,610 --> 00:16:50,820
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>It's time for me to seal this love away</i></font>

240
00:16:51,190 --> 00:16:54,760
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>in my own way. 
In a way that's right for me.</i></font>

241
00:16:56,850 --> 00:17:00,140
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">He did pass the test, but with conditions.</font>

242
00:17:00,490 --> 00:17:02,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Sorry, but I went ahead 
and put him to sleep.</font>

243
00:17:03,420 --> 00:17:07,750
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It seems he already knows plenty of 
ways to process the poison inside him,</font>

244
00:17:07,750 --> 00:17:09,560
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">but they don't do enough yet.</font>

245
00:17:11,540 --> 00:17:15,060
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">At Miss Luna's discretion, she must
extract poison from him when necessary.</font>

246
00:17:15,420 --> 00:17:20,510
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Despite the downsides, he did 
agree fully to that condition.</font>

247
00:17:20,770 --> 00:17:22,800
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Although I won't be nearby,</font>

248
00:17:22,800 --> 00:17:27,410
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'll keep contributing what I can 
to help his magical powers grow.</font>

249
00:17:28,210 --> 00:17:30,860
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I did switch sides to support him, 
so I need to own that.</font>

250
00:17:31,820 --> 00:17:35,200
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Thank you for your 
judgment, Wind Magician.</font>

251
00:17:35,200 --> 00:17:38,280
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I am truly glad that you 
were the first judge.</font>

252
00:17:38,570 --> 00:17:41,710
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You've got a sick sense 
of humor, Master Bird.</font>

253
00:17:41,710 --> 00:17:44,630
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Cold as ice. As if you have any 
idea what I've been through.</font>

254
00:17:46,060 --> 00:17:46,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Don't I?</font>

255
00:17:47,470 --> 00:17:49,340
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">U-Um...</font>

256
00:17:50,670 --> 00:17:52,310
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Thank you very much!</font>

257
00:17:53,220 --> 00:17:59,990
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I am also very grateful that you were 
the one to do this, Wind Magician.</font>

258
00:18:01,500 --> 00:18:03,010
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's Gus.</font>

259
00:18:03,240 --> 00:18:08,290
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It ain't "Wind Magician." 
My name is Gustave.</font>

260
00:18:08,290 --> 00:18:12,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Come on, how many times do I have to 
tell you to call me "Gus," Miss Luna?</font>

261
00:18:10,340 --> 00:18:12,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}Oh. Huh?</font>

262
00:18:12,960 --> 00:18:14,940
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">G... Gu—</font>

263
00:18:14,940 --> 00:18:15,970
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Wagyu?</font>

264
00:18:16,900 --> 00:18:20,030
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Well, whatever. I'll be in touch.</font>

265
00:18:20,680 --> 00:18:25,170
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm off then. I'm still a hugely popular 
guy with a ton of stuff on my plate.</font>

266
00:18:25,170 --> 00:18:28,440
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">U-Um, G-Gu... Gu...</font>

267
00:18:28,440 --> 00:18:29,220
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Huh?</font>

268
00:18:29,590 --> 00:18:30,870
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Take care of yourself.</font>

269
00:18:31,180 --> 00:18:32,540
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">She gave up.</font>

270
00:18:33,220 --> 00:18:38,190
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Miss Luna, I'll see you and Lize soon 
enough when I get too much poison.</font>

271
00:18:38,190 --> 00:18:39,590
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Use your shrooms on me then, okay?</font>

272
00:18:39,870 --> 00:18:44,850
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I really like those mushrooms 
of yours, Miss Luna!</font>

273
00:18:44,850 --> 00:18:46,190
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Bye-bee!</font>

274
00:18:47,740 --> 00:18:51,600
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'll be expecting you, Gustave.</font>

275
00:18:52,020 --> 00:18:55,090
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You should've said it when 
he was close enough to hear.</font>

276
00:18:56,070 --> 00:18:59,610
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh, I think he heard her just fine.</font>

277
00:19:01,940 --> 00:19:02,730
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">See?</font>

278
00:19:54,300 --> 00:19:57,150
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Please don't cry, Miss Witch.</i></font>

279
00:19:57,670 --> 00:19:58,990
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>It's okay.</i></font>

280
00:19:59,380 --> 00:20:05,180
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I'm done obsessing over things I've 
lost and letting myself drown in grief.</i></font>

281
00:20:05,890 --> 00:20:11,670
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I'll make peace with my hardship here 
in this forest of gentle mushrooms,</i></font>

282
00:20:12,140 --> 00:20:13,930
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>where you protect me.</i></font>

283
00:20:14,690 --> 00:20:19,930
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>And someday in the future, 
I know I will find love.</i></font>

284
00:20:22,210 --> 00:20:24,010
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Good morning.</font>

285
00:20:24,010 --> 00:20:25,740
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Um, Miss Witch?</font>

286
00:20:26,990 --> 00:20:30,520
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It sort of feels like my 
clothes got bigger on me.</font>

287
00:20:30,520 --> 00:20:32,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Um, I...</font>

288
00:20:37,730 --> 00:20:41,260
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Now they fit perfectly! 
Thank you very much!</font>

289
00:20:44,190 --> 00:20:48,720
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>No matter how many times they're 
erased, I still secretly remember,</i></font>

290
00:20:49,810 --> 00:20:52,600
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>with the help of my faithful 
little mushroom friend,</i></font>

291
00:20:53,010 --> 00:20:56,170
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>my feelings for her that 
I talked about every night.</i></font>

292
00:20:56,980 --> 00:21:00,980
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>My transforming little friend 
telepathically remembers for me</i></font>

293
00:21:00,980 --> 00:21:06,240
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>all those beloved memories 
that spilled from my fingers.</i></font>

294
00:21:12,450 --> 00:21:15,030
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I don't care if this 
love is never fulfilled.</i></font>

295
00:21:15,730 --> 00:21:17,690
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I will carry it with me always.</i></font>

296
00:21:18,370 --> 00:21:21,990
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Love is the source of 
a white witch's magic.</i></font>

297
00:21:22,330 --> 00:21:27,150
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I want to protect her. I want 
to become a strong magician.</i></font>

298
00:21:27,530 --> 00:21:30,820
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>To that end, this is a secret and 
indispensable source of power.</i></font>

299
00:21:31,430 --> 00:21:36,450
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>No kind of magic or turn of fate 
can take this away from me.</i></font>

300
00:21:37,400 --> 00:21:39,400
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I will accept losing some things.</i></font>

301
00:21:39,790 --> 00:21:42,260
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>When I am worn down,
I will strengthen my resolve.</i></font>

302
00:21:40,140 --> 00:21:41,990
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}Hey! Over here, over here!</font>

303
00:21:42,810 --> 00:21:47,530
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I will treasure these moments, 
even if I will eventually forget them.</i></font>

304
00:21:43,310 --> 00:21:45,460
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}Outta my way, ass.</font>

305
00:21:47,870 --> 00:21:51,530
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Perhaps someday, the memories that
 I've spilled will find new life</i></font>

306
00:21:48,170 --> 00:21:50,140
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}Want me to hang one up?</font>

307
00:21:51,530 --> 00:21:54,050
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>and live on, shining within
someone else's heart.</i></font>

308
00:21:54,580 --> 00:21:56,670
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>The lingering echoes 
of these quiet moments</i></font>

309
00:21:56,670 --> 00:22:00,470
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>and the feelings and friendships 
that they nurtured,</i></font>

310
00:22:00,470 --> 00:22:02,550
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>give me the strength to continue.</i></font>

311
00:22:03,130 --> 00:22:07,570
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>So no matter how many times I have 
to start again, I will never give up.</i></font>

312
00:22:08,330 --> 00:22:11,710
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>While living together with
 the witch who will never find love,</i></font>

313
00:22:12,980 --> 00:22:16,970
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I will make my way toward adulthood.</i></font>

314
00:22:25,530 --> 00:22:30,450
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}TRANSLATION: MICHAEL ARNOLD</font>

315
00:22:30,780 --> 00:22:35,620
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}SUBTITLE TIMING: ANDY ELLIS
EDITING: ELISABETH CRIST</font>

316
00:22:36,040 --> 00:22:40,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}QUALITY CHECK: GABRIELLA ALABANZA
TRANSLATION CHECK: MICHELLE TYMON</font>

